Parameter.Name: Epoch
Parameter.Caveats: This parameter exhibits an increasing monotonic progression

Parameter.Name: Frame Number
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH

Parameter.Name: Data Quality Flag
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Data Quality Flag, 0 means no Issues
Parameter.Caveats: 32 bit flag used to indicate data quality

Parameter.Name: Half Accumulation Time
Parameter.Description: Period of Time used to accumulate Spectra

Parameter.Name: SSPC
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Caveats: Rebinned, divided by energy bin widths and adjusted to accomodate a per second time scale

Parameter.Name: Energy Level
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Caveats: Center of each slow spectrum channel

Parameter.Name: Channel
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH

Parameter.Name: Bin Width
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH

Parameter.Name: Peak 511
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Peak Location of the 511 keV Line
Parameter.Caveats: This is the detector channel (0-4096) which appears to contain the 511

Parameter.Name: Count Error
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Count Error based on Poisson Statistics
Parameter.Caveats: Error only valid for large count values
